== 擁有權 ==
[[File:Atlantic_Monthly_1857.png|thumb]]]
截至近代幾十年，《大西洋》一直被稱為[[新英格蘭|新英格蘭]]文學雜誌（相對同樣於紐約市出版的《[[哈泼斯杂志|哈帕雜誌]]》及後來的《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》）。它享譽全國，這對許多美國作家及詩人的職業生涯都很重要。在成立第三年，《大西洋》由著名的波士頓出版社{{le|蒂克諾與菲爾德|Ticknor and Fields}}（後來成為該城市以文學文化聞名的{{le|霍頓·米夫林·哈考特|Houghton Mifflin Harcourt}}的一部分。該雜誌於1908年由當時的編輯{{le|埃勒里·塞奇威克|Ellery Sedgwick}}收購，但仍留在波士頓。
1980年，該雜誌被房地產大亨—{{le|波士頓地產|Boston Properties}}的創始人{{le|莫添默·塞克曼|Mortimer Zuckerman}}收購，並成為董事長。1999年9月27日，塞克曼把雜誌的擁有權轉讓予重點關注華盛頓特區和政府的新聞的{{le|大西洋媒體|Atlantic Media}}之擁有人{{le|大衛·G·布拉德利|David G. Bradley}}。布拉德利曾承諾，該雜誌將在可預見的未來留在波士頓，就像接下來的五年半一樣。

然而於2005年4月，出版商宣布，編輯部的辦公室將從他們位於波士頓北華盛頓街77號的長期地點遷出，加入到該公司於華盛頓特區的廣告和發行部門<ref name="leaving city">{{cite news|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304133324/http://www.boston.com/news/local/massachusetts/articles/2005/04/15/atlantic_148_year_institution_leaving_city/|title=Atlantic, 148-year institution, leaving city: Magazine of Twain, James, Howells heads to capital|date=April 15, 2005|last2=Mehegan|first2=David|first1=Mark|last1=Feeney|newspaper=[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]}}</ref>。後來在八月下旬，布拉德利告訴《{{le|紐約觀察家日報|The New York Observer}}》，指此舉並非為了省錢，近期所節省的金額將在20—30萬美元之間，相對與遣散費相關的支出所吞沒的相對較小—但它相反將有助於在華盛頓建立一個樞紐，在此樞紐中，布拉德利擁有出版物的頂尖人物能在大西洋媒體的保護傘下進行合作。波士頓的工作人員少數同意搬遷，布拉德利開始公開尋找新的編輯人員<ref>{{cite news |title=Atlantic owner scours country for cinder-editor |newspaper=[[New_York_Observer|New York Observer]] |date=August 29 – September 5, 2005}}</ref>。

2006年，布拉德利聘請了{{le|詹姆斯·本內特|James Bennet (journalist)}}出任總編輯；他曾擔任《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》耶路撒冷分社社長。他還聘請了包括{{le|傑費理·戈德堡|Jeffrey Goldberg}}及{{le|安德魯·沙利文|Andrew Sullivan}}等一些作者<ref name=Kurtz>{{Cite news | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/08/05/AR2007080501576.html | title = The Atlantic's Owner Ponies Up | first1= Howard |last1=Kurtz | authorlink=Howard Kurtz | date = August 6, 2007 |work=The Washington Post | accessdate =August 18, 2007}}</ref>。傑伊·勞夫（Jay Lauf）於2008年以發行人和副總裁的身份加入該機構；截至2017年，他是《[[石英財經網|石英財經網]]》的發行人兼總裁<ref>{{cite journal |url=https://www.theatlantic.com/a/masthead.mhtml |title=Atlantic masthead |journal=The Atlantic |accessdate=October 7, 2010}}</ref>。

2014年初，本內特及鮑勃·科恩（Bob Cohn）成為《大西洋雜誌》的聯合主席，當本內特被竊聽領導《紐約時報》的社論版面時，科恩於2016年3月成為《大西洋雜誌》的唯一總裁<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/press-releases/archive/2016/03/bob-cohn-named-sole-president-of-the-atlantic/473610/|title=Bob Cohn Named Sole President of The Atlantic; James Bennet to Leadership Post at New York Times|publisher=|date=March 14, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/15/business/media/james-bennet-will-lead-editorial-page-at-new-york-times.html|title=James Bennet Will Lead Editorial Page at New York Times|date=March 14, 2016|work=The New York Times|access-date=May 29, 2018|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>。傑費理·戈德堡於2016年10月被任命為總編輯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/press-releases/archive/2016/10/jeffrey-goldberg-named-editor-in-chief-of-the-atlantic/503576/|title=Jeffrey Goldberg Named Editor in Chief of The Atlantic|publisher=|date=October 11, 2016}}</ref>。

2017年7月28日，《大西洋雜誌》宣布，億萬富翁投資者和慈善家[[勞倫·鮑威爾·喬布斯|勞倫·鮑威爾·喬布斯]]（前[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]總裁兼CEO[[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史提夫·喬布斯]]的遺孀），她透過自己的{{le|愛默生集團|Emerson Collective}}獲得了大部分股權，而愛默生集團的工作人員彼得·拉特曼（Peter Lattman）即時被任命為《大西洋雜誌》的副董事長。大衛·G·布拉德利及大西洋媒體在該次交易中保留了少數股份<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/28/business/media/atlantic-media-emerson-collective-majority-stake.html|title=Laurene Powell Jobs's Organization to Take Majority Stake in The Atlantic|first=Sydney|last=Ember|date=July 28, 2017|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] }}</ref>。

== 政治 ==
縱觀其歷史，《大西洋》一直不願意在選舉中推薦候選人。1860年，即出版三年後，《大西洋》時任編輯{{le|詹姆斯·羅素·洛厄爾|James Russell Lowell}}贊同[[共和黨_(美國)|美國共和黨]]人[[亞伯拉罕·林肯|亞伯拉罕·林肯]]首次競選總統，並贊成[[廢奴主義|廢除奴隸制]]<ref>[[James_Russell_Lowell|Lowell, James Russell]], [https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/1860/10/the-election-in-november/306549/ "The Election in November"], ''The Atlantic'', November 1860.</ref>。

在104年後的1964年，愛德華·懷克斯（Edward Weeks）代表編輯委員會致函贊同[[民主黨_(美國)|美國民主黨]]總統[[林登·约翰逊|林登·莊遜]]，並斥責共和黨人[[貝利·高華德|貝利·高華德]]的參選人資格<ref>Weeks, Edward, [https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/1964/10/the-1964-election/303598/ "The 1964 Election"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/1964/10/the-1964-election/303598/ |date=20210225003913 }}, ''The Atlantic'', November 1964.</ref>。

2016年，編輯委員會自該雜誌創立以來，第三次贊同民主黨總統候選人[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉莉·克林頓]]，因此受到共和黨人[[唐納·川普|當勞·特朗普]]就競選資格的譴責<ref>[https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2016/11/the-case-for-hillary-clinton-and-against-donald-trump/501161/ "Against Donald Trump"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2016/11/the-case-for-hillary-clinton-and-against-donald-trump/501161/ |date=20210208051328 }}, ''The Atlantic'', November 2016.</ref>。選舉後，該雜誌成為了特朗普總統的有力批評者。2019年3月，編輯{{le|雍利·阿貝爾鮑姆|Yoni Appelbaum}}正式呼籲{{le|致力彈劾唐納德·特朗普|Efforts to impeach Donald Trump}}：「現在是國會判斷總統是否適合任職的時候了<ref name=ImpeachDonaldTrump>{{cite news|last1=Appelbaum|first1=Yoni|title=Impeach Donald Trump|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2019/03/impeachment-trump/580468/|accessdate=17 January 2019|website=The Atlantic|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227204017/https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2019/03/impeachment-trump/580468/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/the-atlantic-calls-for-impeachment-as-mainstream-media-continues-to-lead-charge-against-trump The Atlantic calls for impeachment as mainstream media continues to lead charge against Trump] {{Wayback|url=https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/the-atlantic-calls-for-impeachment-as-mainstream-media-continues-to-lead-charge-against-trump |date=20210216125937 }} [[Fox_News|Fox News]]</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/the-atlantics-march-cover-makes-the-case-for-trumps-impeachment-2019-1 |title='Impeach': The Atlantic's March cover makes the case for Trump's impeachment |website=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]] |date=January 17, 2019 |accessdate=January 17, 2019 |archive-date=2021-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216130043/https://www.businessinsider.com/the-atlantics-march-cover-makes-the-case-for-trumps-impeachment-2019-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」

== 格式，發布頻率與名稱 ==
《大西洋月刊》每年出版十期，有超過500,000名讀者訂閱<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2001/05/07/business/07ATLA.html?ex=1224129600&en=7a32bba6b6e6f7ff&ei=5070|title=Media Talk: This Summer, It's the Atlantic Not-Monthly|first=Alex|last=Kuczynski|date=May 7, 2001|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=October 7, 2010|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717062535/http://www.nytimes.com/2001/05/07/business/07ATLA.html?ex=1224129600&en=7a32bba6b6e6f7ff&ei=5070|dead-url=no}} 當格式首先從嚴格的月度變化（每年出現12次）到較低的頻率，名稱的改變並沒有正式公布。</ref>。截至2001年為止，該月刊已出版了144年，每年出版10期。自2003年起，它每年出版11期。從2004年1月／2月開始，它從封面上刪除了「月刊」一詞，並在2007年正式更名。《大西洋》的特色文章涉及政治、外交，商業與經濟，文化與藝術，科技和科學等領域<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com|title=The Atlantic|website=The Atlantic|language=en-US|access-date=April 26, 2017|archive-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706231412/https://www.theatlantic.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2008年1月22日，TheAtlantic.com放棄了其訂閱者牆，並容許用戶自由瀏覽其網站，包括所有過去的存檔<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/doc/200801u/editors-note|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509191810/http://www.theatlantic.com/doc/200801u/editors-note|url-status=yes|archive-date=2008-05-09|title=Editors' Note|journal=The Atlantic|accessdate=October 7, 2010}}</ref>。2011年，《大西洋》的網絡媒體資源包括一個於2009年啟動的新聞和意見跟踪網站TheAtlanticWire.com<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.observer.com/2011/01/exclusive-exgawker-guy-snyder-to-head-atlantic-wire-new-manhattan-staff|title=Exclusive: Ex-Gawker Guy Snyder to Head Atlantic Wire, New Manhattan Staff|date=January 31, 2011|author=Summers, Nick|work=The New York Observer|accessdate=March 26, 2012|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731085733/https://observer.com/2011/01/exclusive-exgawker-guy-snyder-to-head-atlantic-wire-new-manhattan-staff/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，及一個於2011年開始運營並致力於全球城市和趨勢的獨立網站TheAtlanticCities.com<ref name="Folio">{{cite news |url=http://www.foliomag.com/2011/atlantic-debuts-atlanticcities-com |title=The Atlantic Debuts TheAtlanticCities.com |work=FOLIO Magazine |date=September 15, 2011 |author=Welton, Caysey |accessdate=March 26, 2012 |archive-date=2016-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405185923/http://www.foliomag.com/2011/atlantic-debuts-atlanticcities-com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據2011年12月的《[[Mashable|Mashable]]》簡介，自2008年初以來，《大西洋》就關閉了付費專區，最近訪問這三個網絡媒體資源的流量每月超過1,100萬，瀏覽量增長了驚人的2,500％<ref>{{cite news |url= http://mashable.com/2011/12/19/the-atlantic-digital-first/ |title= Inside The Atlantic: How One Magazine Got Profitable by Going 'Digital First' |date= December 19, 2011 |work= Mashable |author= Indvik, Lauren |accessdate= March 26, 2012 |archive-date= 2020-12-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201208140631/https://mashable.com/2011/12/19/the-atlantic-digital-first/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2011年12月，TheAtlantic.com上開設了一個新的健康頻道，內容涵蓋食品以及與思想、身體、性愛、家庭和公共衛生有關的主題。它的發布由尼古拉斯·積遜（Nicholas Jackson）監督著，他此前一直監督著生活頻道，他最初加入TheAtlantic.com以報導科技新聞<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.adweek.com/news/technology/atlantic-continues-expansion-health-channel-137022 |title='The Atlantic' Continues Expansion With Health Channel |work=AdWeek |accessdate=March 26, 2012 |date=December 13, 2011 |author=Moses, Lucia |archive-date=2017-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113232327/http://www.adweek.com/news/technology/atlantic-continues-expansion-health-channel-137022 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。TheAtlantic.com還擴展了視覺敘事，此外還增加了由艾倫·泰勒（Alan Taylor）策劃的「聚焦（In Focus）」照片博客<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mediabistro.com/mediajobsdaily/alan-taylor-jumps-to-the-atlantic_b5432 |date=January 19, 2011 |author=Kaufman, Rachel |title=Alan Taylor Jumps to The Atlantic |work=Media Bistro's Media Jobs Daily |accessdate=March 27, 2012 |archive-date=2014-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303165429/http://www.mediabistro.com/mediajobsdaily/alan-taylor-jumps-to-the-atlantic_b5432 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年，它創建了其視頻頻道<ref>{{cite news |url=http://allthingsd.com/20110804/the-atlantic-launches-a-video-aggregator-with-a-twist/ |title=The Atlantic Launches a Video Aggregator With a Twist |work=All Things D. |author=Kafka, Peter |date=August 4, 2011 |accessdate=March 27, 2012 |archive-date=2012-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323130347/http://allthingsd.com/20110804/the-atlantic-launches-a-video-aggregator-with-a-twist/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最初創建作為聚合器，《大西洋》的視頻組件—大西洋工作室（Atlantic Studios），此後在內部製作工作室中發展，以創建自訂視頻系列和原始紀錄片<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.streamingmedia.com/Articles/Editorial/Featured-Articles/The-Atlantic-Adapts-A-Legendary-Magazine-Meets-Online-Video-105232.aspx|title=The Atlantic Adapts: A Legendary Magazine Meets Online Video - Streaming Media Magazine|last=Dreier|first=Troy|work=Streaming Media Magazine|access-date=April 26, 2017|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731085804/https://www.streamingmedia.com/Articles/Editorial/Featured-Articles/The-Atlantic-Adapts-A-Legendary-Magazine-Meets-Online-Video-105232.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年，TheAtlantic.com推出了專門的「科學」版塊<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/science/archive/2015/09/introducing-the-atlantics-new-science-section/405088/|title=Science Has a New Home on TheAtlantic.com|last=Andersen|first=Ross|work=The Atlantic|access-date=April 26, 2017|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208140628/https://www.theatlantic.com/science/archive/2015/09/introducing-the-atlantics-new-science-section/405088/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在2016年1月它重新設計並擴大了其政治版塊，以配合2016年美國總統大選<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/press-releases/archive/2016/01/the-atlantic-launches-politics-policy-expands-coverage-and-events-triples-reporting-team/423087/|title=The Atlantic Launches Politics and Policy Expansion|work=The Atlantic|access-date=April 26, 2017|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921123609/https://www.theatlantic.com/press-releases/archive/2016/01/the-atlantic-launches-politics-policy-expands-coverage-and-events-triples-reporting-team/423087/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年9月，TheAtlantic.com引入了數碼訂閱模式，限制了未訂閱的讀者每月只能瀏覽五篇免費文章<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/press-releases/archive/2019/09/atlantics-new-subscription-plans-and-meter/597418/|title=The Atlantic Launches New Subscription Plans and Introduces A Metered Model|date=2019-09-05|website=The Atlantic|language=en-US|access-date=2019-10-06|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208140650/https://www.theatlantic.com/press-releases/archive/2019/09/atlantics-new-subscription-plans-and-meter/597418/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2019/09/introducing-the-atlantics-new-subscription-model/597304/|title=Introducing The Atlantic's New Subscription Model|last=Goldberg|first=Jeffrey|date=2019-09-05|website=The Atlantic|language=en-US|access-date=2019-10-06|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208140731/https://www.theatlantic.com/news/archive/2019/09/introducing-the-atlantics-new-subscription-model/597304/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

